### Backend
- Data model for Cronjob (first-class object)
  - Fields: id, name, enabled, scheduleExpression, scheduleUI, timezone, triggerType, targetType (agent|workflow), targetId, inputPayloadTemplate, permissionsLevel, automationLevel, constraints, safetyRails, retryPolicy, outputsConfig, ownerId, module, tags, createdAt, updatedAt, lastRun, nextRun
